nimtm - a wrapper for the QBittorrent Web-API

QUICK EXAMPLE

import nimtm
let connection = initQb("http://127.0.0.1:8080", "admin", "adminadmin")
conn.login()
if conn.connected:
  var torrents = conn.getTorrents()
  for torrent in torrents:
    echo getTorrentFiles(torrent["hash"])
